Please download the new  version at https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.anttek.dict.ui2AntTek Dictionary is a free GUI for accessing StarDict dictionary files and other online dictionary services (a dictionary shell). We look at best integration with Android platform.â Fast search online and offline dictionary â Free dictionary data from Market and Internetâ Easy to look up words from other applicationsâ Easy to share by long clickâ Community supportsFeatureâ Look up word definitions with different matching strategy: exact, start with, end with or both.â Compatible with Stardict dataâ Look up from online dictionary including Google Dictionary, Wikipedia, Bing Translate, Google Translate, Abbreviation, Abbreviation Dictionary, Yahoo Spelling Checker, Zachblume Spelling Checker.â Rich and customizable formaters (change text font, text color, background color)â Customize GUI depending on your devices and your preferences (simple view, dual view)â Quick look up allows to quickly find word definitions without interruption of your articles or web pagesDictionary DataApart from online dictionary services, three main offline dictionary sources:- Download free  data from Market:
